      <p class="text-center text-muted" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 48px;">Get any one of these wrong, and your dog could end up in the road, at a neighbor's house, or worse. Here's exactly what happened during 8 weeks of head-to-head testing on a challenging 3-acre property.</p>

