          <div class="factor-header">
            <span class="factor-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Fence Customization &amp; Flexibility</h3>
              <span class="factor-verdict verdict-spoton">Winner: SpotOn</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Your property isn't a perfect square &mdash; and a GPS fence that can't match your real boundaries leaves dangerous gaps. That pond, that driveway, that garden with toxic plants? If your fence can't trace around them precisely, your dog is exposed.</p>
          <div class="vs-grid">
            <div class="vs-card vs-winner">
              <h4>SpotOn Flexibility</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Unlimited fences from &#8531; acre to 100,000+ acres</li>
                <li>Up to 1,500 virtual fence posts per zone</li>
                <li>Complex, irregular shapes by walking the boundary</li>
                <li>"Keep Out Zones" within main boundary</li>
                <li>Home Zones prevent indoor corrections</li>
                <li>Works completely off-grid</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-card">
