              <span class="factor-verdict verdict-tie">Close Call</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Here's the uncomfortable truth: the most accurate boundary in the world is useless if your dog ignores it. A dog that blows through its warning zone is a dog that ends up in the street. Both systems take different approaches &mdash; but one gives you far more control when the stakes are highest.</p>
