          <p>Would you pay for a home security system that stops protecting your family the moment you miss a monthly payment? That's exactly what happens with a subscription-dependent GPS fence. Miss a payment, lose your boundary. Your dog's safety &mdash; held hostage by a monthly bill.</p>
