                <li>Silver: $12.99/mo (20 fences)</li>
                <li>Gold: $19.99/mo (unlimited)</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="cost-total">
                <span>3-Year Total:</span>
                <strong>$959 &ndash; $1,319</strong>
