          </div>
          <p><strong>Bottom Line:</strong> Halo's lower $599 upfront price is tempting, but once you factor in the required subscription, every Halo plan costs more than SpotOn over 3 years. With our $80 coupon, SpotOn's $919 one-time cost means no recurring fees and no risk of your collar becoming a paperweight &mdash; and it's cheaper than every Halo subscription tier at 3 years.</p>
